title: The Issues Democrats Can't Censor Will Be Their Downfall with Abe Hamadeh and Rob Collins
itunes:title: The Issues Democrats Can't Censor Will Be Their Downfall with Abe Hamadeh and Rob Collins
description:
New DHS leaks expose the Biden Admin's aggressive experts to control and censor ordinary Americans. But Charlie explains that while you can censor Facebook, you can't censor inflation, you can't censor crime, and you can't censor failure. Rob Collins, founder of the conservative credit card Coign, and Arizona AG nominee Abe Hamadeh join to talk about growing GOP momentum and the potential for massive seat flips all across the country.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
